---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
---

<LandingLayout title="Email Marketing That Actually Gets Opened" description="Squatch Marketing handles your email marketing end-to-end. Campaigns, automation, and reporting for $149/mo. Free 15-minute email audit.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center gradient-mesh noise overflow-hidden">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute top-[10%] right-[5%] w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-teal/[0.09] blur-[160px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="orb-drift-reverse absolute bottom-[8%] left-[0%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-blue/[0.07] blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pt-28 lg:pt-32 pb-16">
      <div class="reveal mb-6">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-blue/[0.08] border border-blue/[0.12]">
          <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue animate-pulse"></div>
          <span class="text-blue text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Free Email Audit</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-display font-800 text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,5rem)] text-white leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.03em] mb-6">
        Email marketing <span class="text-gradient">that actually gets opened.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-10">
        Custom HTML emails, automated lifecycle sequences, and list management done for you. Strategy, design, copywriting, and reporting under one roof. No Mailchimp templates, no guesswork.
      </p>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-12">
        <a href="/request-demo?ref=email" class="btn-gradient px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-white font-semibold text-[15px]">
          <span>Get Your Free Audit</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-ghost px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-white/50 hover:text-white font-medium text-[15px]">
          How It Works
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-800 text-gradient">500+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">Campaigns delivered</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-px h-10 bg-white/[0.08]"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-800 text-white">36K+</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">Campaign clicks generated</div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-px h-10 bg-white/[0.08]"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-800 text-gradient">$36</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1">Avg. ROI per $1 spent</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-void to-transparent pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="relative py-24 bg-void overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal mb-12 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-teal/[0.08] border border-teal/[0.12] mb-5">
          <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal animate-pulse"></div>
          <span class="text-teal text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">How It Works</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white leading-tight">
          Audit. Build. <span class="text-gradient">Measure.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="reveal glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-7">
          <div class="font-display font-800 text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-lg text-white mb-3">Free email audit</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">15-minute look at your current email setup. We identify what's working, what's leaking money, and the 3 things we'd fix first. Delivered as a short video walkthrough.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-7">
          <div class="font-display font-800 text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-lg text-white mb-3">We build your system</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Custom welcome sequences, lifecycle automations, and weekly newsletters built in your brand voice. HTML emails that render cleanly in Outlook, Gmail, and Apple Mail.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-7">
          <div class="font-display font-800 text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-lg text-white mb-3">Launch and measure</h3>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Monthly reporting shows opens, clicks, revenue attributed to email, and what to test next. You see the numbers. We handle the work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-void overflow-hidden">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute top-[20%] left-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-teal/[0.04] blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr] gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="reveal">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-blue/[0.08] border border-blue/[0.12] mb-5">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue animate-pulse"></div>
            <span class="text-blue text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">What You Get</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white leading-tight mb-6">
            A full email program. <span class="text-gradient">Not just templates.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Most small business email is an afterthought. We treat it like the highest-ROI channel it actually is. Strategy, creative, and execution all under one roof.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="reveal glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/[0.1] border border-teal/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-teal font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Welcome + onboarding sequences</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">Automated emails that trigger when someone signs up. Turns cold subscribers into engaged customers in their first 30 days.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/[0.1] border border-teal/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-teal font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Monthly newsletter</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">A branded HTML email sent every month. We write it, design it, and send it. You review before it goes out.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/[0.1] border border-teal/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-teal font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Lifecycle automation</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">Follow-ups after purchase, re-engagement for dormant subscribers, review requests after service. The emails you know you should send but never do.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/[0.1] border border-teal/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-teal font-bold">4</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">List hygiene + deliverability</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">DKIM, SPF, and DMARC setup. Auto-cleanup of bounces and unsubscribes. Your emails land in the inbox, not the spam folder.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/[0.1] border border-teal/[0.15] flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-teal font-bold">5</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-1">Monthly performance report</div>
              <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">Opens, clicks, revenue, what worked, what to try next. Plain-English reporting, not a 40-metric dashboard you won't read.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="relative py-24 section-mesh overflow-hidden">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute top-0 right-[30%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-blue/[0.05] blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal glass-strong rounded-3xl p-10 sm:p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-1/2 bg-gradient-to-bl from-teal/[0.06] to-transparent pointer-events-none rounded-3xl"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-blue/[0.08] border border-blue/[0.12] mb-6">
            <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue animate-pulse"></div>
            <span class="text-blue text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Pricing</span>
          </div>

          <div class="text-white/40 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Starting at</div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="font-display font-800 text-6xl sm:text-7xl text-white">$149</span>
            <span class="text-white/40 text-xl">/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-base mb-8">Starts after your free audit. No contracts. Cancel anytime. Plans scale with list size and campaign frequency.</p>

          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-left mb-10 max-w-md mx-auto">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Monthly newsletter
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Welcome sequences
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Lifecycle automations
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> List management
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Monthly reporting
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 text-sm">
              <span class="text-blue">✓</span> Cancel anytime
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="/request-demo?ref=email" class="btn-gradient px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-white font-semibold text-[15px] inline-block">
            <span>Get Your Free Audit</span>
          </a>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs mt-4">15-minute audit, delivered as a short video. No call required.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-void overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="reveal mb-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white leading-tight">
          Common <span class="text-gradient">questions</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="reveal glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">What if I don't have an email list yet?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">We help you build one. Part of the onboarding is setting up signup forms on your site and collecting emails from your existing customer base. Zero list to start is fine.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Do I need a separate email platform?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">We use Brevo (formerly Sendinblue) for most clients. It's $21-65/mo depending on list size and we handle all setup. If you already use Mailchimp, Klaviyo, or ConvertKit, we work inside your existing account.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">How long before I see results?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Welcome sequences fire day one and start converting new subscribers immediately. Newsletter engagement takes 30-60 days as your list warms up. Revenue attribution kicks in once we've sent 3-4 campaigns.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Who writes the emails?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">We do. Every email is custom-written in your brand voice. You review each one before it goes out. No AI slop, no generic templates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4 glass-interactive rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Can I add SMS or other channels later?</div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Yes. SMS marketing is +$99/mo. Social media content is +$149/mo. We add channels as your business is ready, not all at once.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-void overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="reveal font-display font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Want a free look at your email setup?
      </h2>
      <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-white/50 text-lg mb-8">
        15 minutes. Short video walkthrough. 3 specific fixes. Zero pressure.
      </p>
      <a href="/request-demo?ref=email" class="btn-gradient px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-white font-semibold text-[15px] inline-block">
        <span>Get Your Free Audit</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</LandingLayout>
